name: Cactusucially High
description:
F L Y   H I G H  S H O OT   H I G H 

Instructions: 

  1. WASD - FLOAT MOVEMENTS
  2. SPACE - FLOAT
  3. CTRL - SHOOT
  4. ALT - CHANGE AIM
  5. GOAL: SHOOT THE ENEMIES AND GAIN LOOT: SIZES(HEAT EXPANSION), SPEED, RANGE AND FUEL. IN ORDER TO COMPLETE THE GAME YOU MUST DEFEAT THE BOSS ON THE FINAL LEVEL 5 AREA. DO NOT STAY INSIDE THE FIRE AREA AND OUTSIDE THE SPACE, YOU'LL FALL AND CONTRACT.
  6. HAVE FUN !
